Sun Jun 28 14:35:39 UTC 2026 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 6.9.0:
  * SeleniumLibrary 6.9.0 is a new release with several
    enhancements and bug fixes. A couple new keywords, for drag
    and drop as well as getting css properties, have been added.
    Secret type support has be added. An issue with using lists
    with chaining locators has been fixed. Several of the minimum
    required versions have been updated.
  * SeleniumLibrary supports Python 3.10 through 3.14, Selenium
    4.29.0 through 4.44.0 and Robot Framework 6.1.1 and 7.4.2.

